title: Unity Fellowship Church New York Praise Team Presents"A Holiday Concert" Featuring Manifest
desc:
Unity Fellowship Church New York City is please to invite the public to celebrate the rich and joyous sounds of the season with it annual holiday concert. This year's theme is "We Speak Your Name". Lead by Musical Director Kenneth Smith and featuring mens signing group  Manifest , the event will take place Saturday, December 5, 2015 at 7pm. 
 We invite singers from all faith communities to sign up and participate. ?There is a $ 15.00 registration fee. Rehearsal dates are as follows:? 
 November 10, 17, & 24, 2015 / 7:00-9:00 pm 
 December 1, 2015 / 7:00-9:00 pm 
 December 3, 2015 / Workshop / 5:00-9:00 pm
